articles.title: 'The clubs cannot leave' - Real Madrid president insists Super League will return - The Star Online
articles.description: MADRID (Reuters) -     Real Madrid president Florentino Perez says the 12 clubs who were to found the European Super League cannot abandon it due to binding contracts, and he promised the project would return after a period of reflection.
